<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: bliss lobotomy -->
  <BlissLobotomy.label>极乐切脑</BlissLobotomy.label>
  <!-- EN: Remove part of a person's brain, placing them in a state of bliss while rendering them incapable of intellectual and skilled labor. They will also learn more slowly, and be less likely to rebel or attempt a prison break. -->
  <BlissLobotomy.description>移除人的部分大脑，使其变得无忧无虑，但同时也会丧失从事智识和专业工作的能力。他们的学习速度也会更慢，反抗或越狱的冲动更低。</BlissLobotomy.description>
  <!-- EN: Lobotomizing TargetA. -->
  <BlissLobotomy.jobString>正在对TargetA切脑。</BlissLobotomy.jobString>
  
  <!-- EN: ghoul infusion -->
  <GhoulInfusion.label>食尸鬼转化</GhoulInfusion.label>
  <!-- EN: Infuse a living person with an archotech shard to create a terrifying creature known as a ghoul. Ghouls are ferocious melee fighters and are incapable of work. They eat raw meat to survive but never sleep. Hungry ghouls are dangerous.\n\nGhouls created by this operation will be a part of your colony. -->
  <GhoulInfusion.description>向活人体内植入暗黑超凡碎片和活铁，即可创造出被称为食尸鬼的可怕生物。食尸鬼能够进行凶残的近战攻击，但却无法从事任何工作。它们以生肉为食且不需要睡眠。饥饿的食尸鬼将会变得更加危险。</GhoulInfusion.description>
  <!-- EN: Ghoulizing TargetA. -->
  <GhoulInfusion.jobString>正在将TargetA转化为食尸鬼。</GhoulInfusion.jobString>
  
  <!-- EN: surgical inspection -->
  <SurgicalInspection.label>外科检查</SurgicalInspection.label>
  <!-- EN: An invasive surgery to find any hidden abnormalities within a patient. -->
  <SurgicalInspection.description>对病人进行外科检查手术，可找出其隐瞒的异常，该手术会造成创伤。</SurgicalInspection.description>
  <!-- EN: Surgically inspecting TargetA. -->
  <SurgicalInspection.jobString>正在对TargetA进行外科检查。</SurgicalInspection.jobString>
  
</LanguageData>